68 /* the Field MaKe (Raw) macro */
69 static inline uint32_t CSL_FMKR(uint8_t msb, uint8_t lsb, uint32_t val)
70 {
71  uint32_t mask;
72  uint8_t bits;
73  uint32_t newVal;
74 
75  bits = (msb - lsb + 1U);
76  mask = (1U << bits);
77  mask = mask - 1U;
78 
79  newVal = val & mask;
80 
81  return (newVal << lsb);
82 }
83 
84 /* the Field EXTract (Raw) macro */
85 static inline uint32_t CSL_FEXTR(volatile uint32_t reg, uint8_t msb, uint8_t lsb)
86 {
87  uint32_t mask;
88  uint8_t bits;
89  uint32_t value;
90 
91  bits = (msb - lsb + 1U);
92  mask = (1U << bits);
93  mask = mask - 1U;
94  value = (reg >> lsb) & mask;
95  return value;
96 }
97 
98 /* the Field INSert (Raw) macro */
99 static inline uint32_t CSL_FINSR(volatile uint32_t reg, uint8_t msb, uint8_t lsb, uint32_t val)
100 {
101  uint32_t mask;
102  uint8_t bits;
103  uint32_t value;
104  uint32_t tmp;
105 
106  bits = (msb - lsb + 1U);
107  mask = (1U << bits);
108  mask = mask - 1U;
109  value = (mask << lsb);
110  tmp = (reg & ~value);
111  reg = tmp | CSL_FMKR(msb, lsb, val);
112  return reg;
113 }
